'''Mugaar''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Mugaari]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Mugaar/Legends|Mugaar]]. Most Mugaari were fluent in both Mugaar and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

